            "is_prior_year_field": false,
            "draft_value": "* Restores stability following significant disruptions and workforce losses in the FY2026 budget cycle.\n* Addresses rapid expansion of Chinese space science ambitions that challenge US leadership.\n* Reverses underfunding that threatens peer-reviewed National Academies decadal priorities.",
